summary:
Ignoring all my recent deep posts on this blog...
WATCH GOOD OMENS!!! IT'S SO CUTE AND AMAZING!
It has something for everybody....
body:
Ignoring all my recent deep posts on this blog…

WATCH GOOD OMENS!!! IT’S SO CUTE AND AMAZING!

It has something for everybody. It’s a fun, modern day, angel and demon story, where God is a woman, the angel and the demon have the best friendship (which Neil Gaiman–the writer–, David Tenant, and Michael Sheen have all described as “love” to some capacity, so SUPER GAY SUBTEXT!!!!), Doctor Who references with David Tenant, and QUEEN SONGS! CONSTANTLY!

Lots of fluff and angst and a Benedict Cumberbatch cameo, what more could you need in a show??? Its short too, which is good and bad, but needs love to be renewed!

So good, please watch
